I got this recipe from a watier on the greek island of samosThey use it as a spread for bread there butit is excellent ogyro's as well. By the way, the actual name is tzatzikiHere is the recipeyoghurt, chopped garlic, peeled chopped cucumber, salt, whitpepper, a little olive oil and a little vinegarI would love to hear of any other good greek recipes out there--Jon Walkejowalker@oboe.calpoly.ed